imdb.plot outline: Fun Arts Afterschool T.V. Show was created to help students define good morals and to have an increased desire to learn primary school subjects : Health and Fitness, American History, Math, Science, Literacy, Geography, and Social Studies. The show was also created to provide summer learning for students who are not academically on grade level. The format of the show consists of 5-6 comedic segments and 2-3 comedic commercials, that are combined into one episode. Each episode is approximately 25 minutes in length, and designed for both children and adolescents.
